Subject: [PATCH v4 26/28] KVM: TDX: Guard VM state transitions with "all" the locks
From: Sean Christopherson <seanjc@google.com>
To: Marc Zyngier <maz@kernel.org>, Oliver Upton <oliver.upton@linux.dev>, 
